name: The Ocean
description:
Q) What is your name? 
A) J3rett.

Q) Where do you come from? 
A) Born in Boston MA USA, now live in New York, NY USA.

Q) What do you do? 
A) Art & Technology.

Q) Think of a very special place in your mind. What is the name of this place, and what four colours do you associate with it?
A) The ocean — my signature color rich electric blue color code: #0892D0, and maybe a seafoam green, white, waves breaking, and sunset color(s) reflecting on the ocean. 

Q) What three words would you use to describe this special place?
A) Abundant, meditative, free.
